<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>B</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa kan in thangthat, Lei le Van ser-tu
 Bawipa kan in thangthat, Thangthat tlak Pathian
 Bawipa kan in thangthat, Zei-zong te Uk-tu
 Bawipa kan in thangthat, Thangthat tlak Pathian.

[P1]
   Bawipa, Kan in thangthat
   Cunnung bik, Siangpahrang, kan in thangthat
   Aw, Lei le Van Sertu, Aw, Zeizong te Uktu
   Aw, Thangthat awk tlak, Kan Pathian.

[C1]
   Maw Bawipa, Kan in thangthat
   Zeizong vialte, Chung i a um Pathian
   Maw Bawipa, Kan in thangthat
   Zeizong, te uktu, kan Pathian.
   (A AMEN, A MEN) 2

[V2]
 Liangngannak le Thawnnak, Nangmah ta an, si
 Zeizong vialte cungah, Cungnung bik na si
 Sunparnak le Teinak, Nangmah ta an, si
 Zeizong vialte cungah, Cung nung bik na si.

[P2]
   Bawipa, Kan in thangthat
   Cungnung bik, Siangpahrang, kan in thangthat
   Aw, Lei le Van sertu, Aw, Zeizong te Uktu
   Aw, Thangthat awk tlak, Kan Pathian.</lyrics>
<title>BAWIPA KAN IN THANGTHAT</title>
</song>